        "action": "Change City Status decision process",
        "additional_details": "We the undersigned call upon the Government to change the process in which towns can be upgraded to City Status.\r\nCity status is a rare, distinct honour granted by a Monarch, but the process of elevation rests in the hands of the Government.\r\nWe urge the Government to look into the entire process and create proper and binding guidelines.\r\n",
